<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> kopparakecaripa<hi rend="grantha">nma</hi> rāṉa <hi rend="grantha">śrīrāje</hi>n=ti racoḻa<hi rend="grantha">de</hi> varkku yāṇṭu 3<g ref="sym:dash" type="punctuation"/>Āvatu <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yaṅkoṇṭacoḻamaṇṭalattu paṉaiyūrnāṭṭu
<lb n="2"/>vāvalūrnāṭṭut tevatāna n=ti ruvāmāttūruṭaiya pa<hi rend="grantha">ramasvāmi</hi> kaḷukku Uṭaiyār <hi rend="grantha">śrīrājentra</hi> coḻa<hi rend="grantha">de</hi> var perun=ta rattu <hi rend="grantha">se</hi> nāpati
<lb n="3"/><hi rend="grantha">rājentra</hi> coḻa <hi rend="grantha">brahmam(ā) hārā</hi> yar kar<hi rend="grantha">mi</hi> tirumuṉaippāṭi kiḻāṉmurnāṭṭuc ciṟuputtūrp putuvaiyuṭaiyāṉ kan=ta ṉ Aṭaikkala n=ti ru
<lb n="4" break="no"/>vāmāttūruṭaiyārkku vaitta tirunon=tā viḷak koṉṟiṉukku vaitta cāvā muvāp perāṭu toṇṇūṟṟāṟu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Ivvāṭu toṇṇū
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṟṟāṟuṅ koṇṭu pāṭṭañceytu nicatam Uḻakku ney yaṭṭakkaṭavāṉ Ivvūr maṉṟāṭi Aṅki cen=ta ṉ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Ivaṉukkup puṇai Ittiruvāmā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ttūruṭaiyārkku muṉ pāṭṭañ ceytuvarukiṉṟa Ivvūr maṉṟāṭikaḷe <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Itu can=ta rātittaval <hi rend="grantha">panmā heśvara rakṣai <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></hi> 
</p>

